            (sStar == 2 && pStar == 4) || (sStar == 4 && pStar == 2) -> "They are two positions apart within the Zodiac, and such Signs tend to share karmic ties and a deep mutual understanding. These particular two Signs have much in common: Both prize security in a love relationship above almost all else; both tend to be nurturers (Cancer is emotionally nurturing while Taurus loves to spoil their lover with sensual delights, gifts and good, rich meals). They’re both quite domestic and love a quiet night spent at home with their sweetie.\n" +
