            (sStar == 2 && pStar == 6) || (sStar == 6 && pStar == 2) -> "Both of these Signs employ practicality in their daily lives as the most efficient means to most problems. They can be quite sincere and devoted to one another; as people, both have a great deal of integrity. Virgo likes Taurus’s strength and dedication while Taurus appreciates Virgo’s quick mind.\n" +
