            (sStar == 2 && pStar == 7) || (sStar == 7 && pStar == 2) -> "These two Signs are thought of as being karmically linked. They’re both looking for security in a relationship and they share a love of art, poetry and culture. This relationship may start slowly as, on the surface, they might have few common interests. However, once they understand one another they may learn they have much more in common than was first apparent.\n" +
