            (sStar == 3 && pStar == 3) -> "This relationship can never be dull, which is a good thing — these two can get bored easily! Since they have the same need for intellectual stimulation and nearly-constant chatter, they serve very well as one another’s sounding boards off which to bounce new ideas and theories. Gemini is all about freedom and variety of expression, and two Geminis together will enjoy this to the fullest. Others enjoy two Geminis as a couple as well — they’re sure to be the life of every party with their sharp wit and well-honed entertainment routine. If they can avoid competition and cooperate instead, their love relationship can be extremely happy and mutually satisfying.\n" +
