            (sStar == 3 && pStar == 6) || (sStar == 6 && pStar == 3) -> "Virgo may be a bit too serious and demanding for Gemini, especially if this occurs early in the relationship before Gemini has fully committed. If Virgo just gives it time, things will smooth out.\n" +
