            (sStar == 5 && pStar == 6) || (sStar == 6 && pStar == 5) -> "This is a relationship that evolves over time, each partner gradually understanding and appreciating the other. Leo is extroverted, dominant, and charismatic, and often has a short fuse. Virgo is studious and withdrawn, possessed of more versatility than Leo. Although there are differences, they make a wonderful love match when each partner warms up to the other’s unfamiliar style.\n" +
