            (sStar == 5 && pStar == 8) || (sStar == 8 && pStar == 5) -> "They are well tuned in to one another’s needs; Scorpio demands respect and to be wanted while Leo needs to be adored and complimented constantly. They are both extremely loyal, and often possessive of one another. Both members of this love match are able to give the other what they need and while enjoying one another’s strengths.\n" +
